A cubist-style self-portrait in the manner of Pablo Picasso, featuring a fragmented human face with geometric shapes, multiple perspectives shown simultaneously, bold angular features split across different planes, one eye facing forward while another gazes sideways, warm earth tones mixed with muted blues and terracotta oranges, abstract facial elements reassembled in an artistic deconstruction, painted with visible brushstrokes on textured canvas, artistic and contemplative mood, museum-quality fine art aesthetic.
